# Example of a trouble ticket impacting multiple entities
<troubleticket/TT-20240120-001_extra_node_1> noria:troubleTicketImpacts <application/CorporateDNS_extra_node_1> .
<troubleticket/TT-20240120-001_extra_node_1> noria:troubleTicketImpacts <resource/DNS01_extra_node_1> .
