    noria:problemResponsibility <kos/TroubleTicket/problemResponsibility/ManagedBackboneNetworks_extra_node_1> .

# Example of a change request being regulated
<changerequest/CR-20240120-001_extra_node_1> noria:changeRequestIsRegulated true .

