# Example of an alarm being mitigated by a procedure execution container (e.g., a change request)
<eventrecord/DNSOutageAlarm-20240120-0900_extra_node_1> noria:alarmMitigatedBy <changerequest/CR-20240120-001_extra_node_1> .


